Contact us for an unforgettable getaway at Key Largo, FLORIDA
An oasis of comfort and convenience, Playa Largo Resort and Spa from Marriot's Autograph Collection is the perfect place to stay for vacations and business travel alike. Located right off the scenic Overseas Highway and neighboring the famed John Pennekamp Coral Reef State Park, our property is a premier, oceanfront standout among Key Largo resorts and lodgings.
Get in touch and make your reservations at our family-friendly island retreat in Key Largo. Call us at
305.853.1001
or email
info@playalargoresort.com
to make a booking. Embrace the island life and Keys longstanding tradition of unhurried pleasure at Playa Largo.

Celebrate with a getaway in the Florida Keys
PLAY IN THE SAND AND MAKE THE MOST OF YOUR ISLAND TIME AT PLAYA LARGO
Festive fun-filled events are part of our signature experiences at Playa Largo Resort & Spa. Whether you're planning a couples getaway or family vacation, Playa Largo offers endless opportunities to live on island time and connect with the inspirational beauty of the Florida Keys through sustainable and unique experiences.
View Year-Round Fun and Excitement in Key Largo Large
Year-Round Fun and Excitement in Key Largo
From festive holiday events to daily activities, there's always something happening at our resort. Enjoy thrilling tours, relaxing cruises, family-friendly excursions, and special celebrations throughout the year. Whether you're visiting for a seasonal event or just looking to enjoy the area's natural beauty, our resort offers endless adventures for every guest.
